xl bg-amber-50 text-amber-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></div><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"flex w-full items-start justify-between gap-4 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\"><span>What does James mean?</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-up h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m18 15-6-6-6 6\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"mt-3 block text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\">James is a meaningful name that carries a positive origin and cultural significance.</div></div></div></section></div><section class=\"bg-slate-50 py-12\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex flex-col justify-between gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-end\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-4 w-4 text-blue-700\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg>Christian Name Guides</div><h2 class=\"nv-display mt-5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-4xl\">Continue your name research</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-base\">More expert NameVerse guides to help you compare meanings, origins and naming decisions.</p></div><a class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-blue-700\" href=\"/blog\">View all guides<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><article class=\"group overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl \"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br h-56\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 18% 18%, rgba(255,255,255,0.95) 0 10%, transparent 11%), linear-gradient(135deg, #DBEAFE, #C7D2FE)\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-30\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.12) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.10) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:32px 32px\"></div><div class=\"absolute -right-8 -bottom-10 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-white/30 blur-2xl\"></div><div class=\"relative flex h-full items-center justify-between px-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-8 w-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"color:#3730A3\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-6xl font-black tracking-tight opacity-25\" style=\"color:#3730A3\">RC</span></div></div><div class=\"p-5\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\"><span class=\"rounded-full bg-blue-50 px-3 py-1 text-blue-700\">Christian Names</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg>8 min read</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg>27K<!-- --> views</span></div><h3 class=\"nv-display text-xl font-semibold leading-tight text-slate-950 group-hover:text-blue-700 line-clamp-2\">Rare Christian Names With Beautiful Meanings</h3><p class=\"mt-3 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">Explore rare Christian names that carry profound spiritual significance and timeless beauty. From forgotten biblical names to lesser-known saint names, find distinctive options for your baby.</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg>NameVerse Editorial Team</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-700\">Read<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3.5 w-3.5 transition group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></span></div></div></article></div></div></section></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 text-white\"><img alt=\"NameVerse logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/logo.png\"/></div><div><div class=\"text-lg font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950\">NameVerse</div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\">Meanings, origins &amp; guides</div></div></a><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">NameVerse helps parents and researchers discover baby names with meanings, cultural origins, linguistic context and trusted naming guidance.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex gap-2\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/NameVerseOfficial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 transi